<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-15-0696 </DOCNO><TEXT>The report surveys and presents the solar energy projects at the OsloUniversity (Norway) in 1986, which are as follows: 1. Data recordingof the solar plant in a university building. 2. Solar energy houses inDrammen. 3. Calculations and measurements of heat losses in solar collectors.4. Design and test results for the solar heating plants in Moss. 5. Recordinginstruments and systems for the solar heated houses in Moss. 6. Studieson the use of solar energy in agriculture. 7. Studies on the productionmethods for solar heating systems in Switzerland and Austria. 22 drawings,2 tables, 24 references.</TEXT></DOC>